<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4776093>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Flower, fruit and indument of Urtica: A, mature achene of U. dioica subsp. dioica (Henning & Schneider 313, B). B, mature achene of U. magellanica (Weigend 6078-C). C, nearly mature achene of U. mollis (Ricardi et al. 720). D, same, as enclosed in densely pubescent perianth (Ricardi et al. 720). E, sparsely pubescent adaxial leaf lamina of U. magellanica (Gunckel 46.420). F, sparsely pubescent adaxial leaf surface of U. magellanica (Riquelme 18). G, sparsely long-pubescent abaxial leaf surface of U. magellanica (Riquelme 18). H, densely pubescent adaxial leaf surface of U. mollis (Villagrán 1827). I, densely pubescent abaxial leaf surface of U. mollis (Villagrán 1827)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4776093/files/figure.png" .

