        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 4. Urtica mollis Steud. and “U. buchtienii Ross”. A, high-alpine, juvenile plant (just beginning to flower) corresponding to the type of “U. buchtienii” (Sparre 17160). B, typical, unbranched form of of U. mollis corresponding to the type specimens (Arroyo 81901)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4776101/files/figure.png" .

